
Tristan, Logan, Hayden, and Conrad came rushing out of the hotel at that moment, heaving in exertion. "Where did she go?" Hayden asked.
"Sakura," Conrad said softly.
On the corner of the street, Sakura turned her head and peeked at the brothers standing there amongst the crowd, looking as if they have lost all hope.
"I'm sorry," she whispered, tears in her eyes. "I'm so sorry."